p.k: When the body of eminent lawyer Anaan Kamel is found washed up by an underground river, suspicion falls on Marcus Layton, a former employee of the victim's chambers who was recently fired. Part 1/2. Buried: Part 1 (2015). Cast: Stephen Tompkinson, Andrea Lowe, Caroline Catz, Jack Deam, Danny Rahim. Director: Craig Pickles.
